title: OnePlus 12 AQUA TOUCH Glass vs iPhone 15 Pro
description: Its time to Durability Test the OnePlus 12. Get a 4-week trial, free postage, and a digital scale at  Thanks to Stamps.com for sponsoring the show! The OnePlus 12 has a new feature called Aqua Touch - which supposedly allows their new flagship smartphone to work in wet environments or even in the rain. Today we put the OnePlus Aqua touch Glass up against a $1300 dollar Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra, and an iPhone 15 Pro to see which smartphone can truly win smartphone of the year in Atlantis.
